reviewText: This is the pilot episode where Walker is first teamed up with Trivette after Walker's partner is killed during a bank heist.  In the opening scene Walker shows that one ranger is all that is needed to catch criminals.  Walker goes after the robbers for the death of the ranger and finds out that there is a master heist being planned.  Walker ends up alone when misdirection is used to confuse the police and rangers to a bank on one side of city when the real heist in being committed on the other side of the city.  Also Walker agrees to take part in a charity rodeo and Trivette is a clown.
Great show. I am a big Chuck Norris fan so I am so happy to have this. Walker Texas Ranger is still my favorite show.
